      <modifierGroups>
        <modifierGroup>
          <comment>Logic to allow for Command Card: Kampfgruppe von Swoboda Luftwaffe 2cm Flak, &quot;You may take an additional 2cm Light AA platoon with the above ratings if you have already taken a Support 8.8cm Heavy AA Platoon.&quot;.</comment>
