                            <profile id="2d2e-306a-5d77-5287" name="Heer Panzer Division Sd Kfz 251 Half-track Transport" hidden="false" typeId="5cbd-556d-67b5-1bd9" typeName="Command Card">
                              <characteristics>
                                <characteristic name="Info" typeId="bd5c-655e-1889-6af7">A panzer division&apos;s Panzergrenadier Regiment also used Sd Kfz 251 half-tracks to tow their 7.5cm PaK 40 anti-tank guns.</characteristic>
                                <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">This Gun Unit may add an Sd Kfz 251 half-track transport Attachment. The number of vehicles in the Unit is as follows:
•	Add one Sd Kfz 251 (MG) half-track transport for each Gun Team in the Unit.
The characteristics of an SdKfz 251 half-track transport are shown on the Sd Kfz 251 half-track transport (LG295) card. The Transport Attachment loses Mounted Assault and Passenger 3, and gains Tractor:
Tractor: Can carry one Gun Team as Passengers.</characteristic>
                                <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="75a6-20ee-1c76-640a">German, Build, Unit (7.5cm Tank-hunter Platoon)</characteristic>
                              </characteristics>
                            </profile>
