                            <profile id="8dba-a2d1-d06c-e349" name="Waffen-SS Sd Kfz 251 Half-Track Transport" hidden="false" typeId="5cbd-556d-67b5-1bd9" typeName="Command Card">
                              <characteristics>
                                <characteristic name="Info" typeId="bd5c-655e-1889-6af7">In a SS panzer division’s Panzergrenadier Regiment, the 7.5cm PaK 40 anti-tank gun were often towed by armoured Sd Kfz251 half-tracks.</characteristic>
                                <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">This Gun Unit may add an SdKfz 251 half-track transport Attachment. Then number of vehicles in the Unit is as follows:
•	Add one Sd Kfz 251 (MG) half-track transport for each Gun Team in the Unit.
The characteristics of an SdKfz 251 half-track transport are shown on the Sd Kfz 251 SS half-track transport (LG438) card. The Transport Attachment loses Mounted Assault and Passenger 3, and gains Tractor:
Tractor: Can carry one Gun Team as Passengers.</characteristic>
                                <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="75a6-20ee-1c76-640a">German, Build, Unit (7.5cm SS Tank-hunter Platoon)</characteristic>
                              </characteristics>
                            </profile>
