          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Info" typeId="bd5c-655e-1889-6af7">2. Panzerdivision also had two companies of StuG G assault guns in its Panzer IV battalion. These fought as part of Kampfgruppe Holtmeyer who attempted to relieve the lead groups of the division when they were threatened by encirclement.</characteristic>
