          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Info" typeId="bd5c-655e-1889-6af7">Peiper placed the greatest responsibilities on the 6th and 7th SS Panzer Companies and their trusty Panzer IV tanks. These smaller tanks navigated the narrow roads much better than the heavier Panthers.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Your Force includes a Panzer IV SS Tank Company, which is a Formation containing:
• 1	 Panzer IV SS Tank Company HQ (LG195)
