          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Info" typeId="bd5c-655e-1889-6af7">The Panzer IV/70 tank destroyers of SS-Panzerjager-Abteilung 1 formed the armoured core of Kampfgruppe Hansen, often serving as the vanguard for the force.</characteristic>
