          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Info" typeId="bd5c-655e-1889-6af7">Because of its mobility, Schnellgruppe (Fast Group) Knittel ended up serving as a fire brigade in support of Kampfgruppe Peiper&apos;s advance.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Your Force includes one SS Schnellgruppe Knittel, which is a Formation containing:
• 1	 HQ Unit of 1x Puma (5cm) from (LG445) for 2 points
			or 1x Sd Kfz 250 (MG) from (LG223) for 1 point.
