        <selectionEntry id="6ef8-a477-dcc2-e177" name="512. Schwere Panzerjager Abteilung 2nd Company" publicationId="3bbf-3707-35dd-b1f5" page="90" hidden="false" collective="false" import="true" type="unit">
      <profiles>
        <profile id="cf87-9db0-ab11-58a9" name="512. Schwere Panzerjager Abteilung 2nd Company" hidden="false" typeId="5cbd-556d-67b5-1bd9" typeName="Command Card">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Info" typeId="bd5c-655e-1889-6af7">Though from the same battalion, the first and second companies’ compositions were different. The 2nd Company, under the legendary Otto Carius, was made up of crews who reluctantly transitioned from turreted tanks like the Tiger to the Jagdtiger.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">All Units in this Formation have the following ratings for -2 points per Jagdtiger and -1 point per anti-aircraft tank:
Motivation: 5+	Skill: 4+
Counterattack 6	Assault 5+
Last Stand 4+

Other units in this Formation retain their original ratings.
(LFTF): This card does not apply to Panzer IV or StuGTank Platoons.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="75a6-20ee-1c76-640a">German, Build, Formation (Jagdtiger Tank-hunter Company), Title</characteristic>
