        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">This Unit has the following characteristics for no cost:TACTICALTERRAIN DASHCROSS COUNTRY DASHROAD DASHCROSS2&quot;/5cm2&quot;/5cm4&quot;/10cm6&quot;/15cm5+WeaponRangeROF HaltedROF MovingAnti- tankFire- power7.5cm gun64&quot;/160cmARTILLERY24+or Direct Fire32&quot;/80cm21123+LFTF: The 7.5cm gun has the Forward Firing rule for both the artillery and direct fire. It does not have the Brutal, Slow Firing, Smoke, or Smoke Bombardment rules.</characteristic>
