      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Infantry Teams from this Unit become Unarmoured Tank Teams with a Save of 4+ and the movement and special rules below. Discard this card at the start of any Movement Step to revert them to Infantry Teams.TACTICALTERRAIN DASHCROSS COUNTRY DASHROAD DASHCROSS-10&quot;/25cm16&quot;/40cm40&quot;/100cm4+SPECIAL RULESUnarmoured: Team cannot Charge into Contact and must Break Off if Assaulted.</characteristic>
