      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">All Infantry Units in this Formation have the following ratings for:Volksgrenadier UnitFull StrUnder StrAssault Platoon+4 points+3 pointsRifle Platoon+3 points+3 pointsMOTIVATIONCONFIDENT4+Third ReichLast Stand 3+SKILLVETERAN3+IS HIT ONCAREFUL4+Heavy Weapons are rated Assault 4+.You must use this card in conjunction with the other 12. Volksgrenadierdivision command cards.LFTF: The Volksgrenadier Company HQ is upgraded at no cost. This does not apply to sMG42 Machine-gun and 8cm Mortar Platoons.</characteristic>
