      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Any Unit from this Formation whose Unit Leader is within 6”/15cm and Line of Sight of this Formation Commander passes Tactics on a 2+.In Assaults, this Formation Commander Hits on a roll of 2+. When conducting a joint Assault all Infantry Teams in the Assaulting Units hit on a roll of 2+.</characteristic>
